sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Client
    participant MissionController
    participant MissionService
    participant G3UserClient
    participant G3 as G3 User Service
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    Client->>MissionController: POST /api/g4/missions JWT
    MissionController->>MissionService: create
    MissionService->>MissionService: assertVehicleAvailable 409
    alt G3 validation enabled
        MissionService->>G3UserClient: assertDriverExists
        G3UserClient->>G3: GET /api/users/drivers/ids
        G3-->>G3UserClient: driver ids list
    end
    MissionService->>DB: save Mission
    MissionService-->>Client: 201 Created
